data.description: WOW! what a wonderful remodeled manufactures home It's on it's own lot, with the Gulf course as your back yard. A beautiful patio faces North so it is well shaded, your could set in comfort and enjoy the view of the golf course, This 3 bd, 2 ba. home has a Large living  room and a Dining room area with built in Hutch, a large pantry in kitchen fully remodeled, newer self close cabinets with granite counter tops,newer appliance and a kitchen island. Large Master bedroom with an over size walk in closet, master bath has a separate remodeled shower, dual sink, house has water proof laminated floor and tile in the bathrooms. Separate huge Laundry room with sink,lots of cabinets, built in desk and a closeth.Alarm will not remain in the property.
